		description="The intrusive thoughts had seemed like corrosion in a deep layer of yourself. Then they were gone. Not suppressed. Not argued into silence. Rewritten. Humans are usually background animals with jobs, faces, and repeating complaints. You could not tell two apart if you cared to try, and caring to try has rarely been useful. But the same tissue that produces all that noise may have a surface your neuroweave can touch."
